text: Björn Engholm (born 9 November 1939) is a Lübeck born German SPD politician. He was Minister-President of Schleswig-Holstein from 1988 to 1993 and leader of the Social Democratic Party of Germany between 1991 and 1993.. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Politicians of the Social Democratic Party of Germany Category:Politicians from Schleswig-Holstein Category:People from Lübeck Category:Living people Category:Agriculture ministers of Germany Category:Education ministers of Germany
